  "title": "Tapping for the feast-or-famine swing",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute script for the roller coaster of big inflows and scary gaps.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 4 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program. The script targets the feast-or-famine cycle: money rushes in and drains out, never quite landing on stable ground. Use in the gap periods, when the last flush has faded and the next payment hasn't arrived.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 4 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"End the feast/famine cycle.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
