          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 4 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program. The script targets the feast-or-famine cycle: money arrives in a rush, then drains out, then the wait for the next wave. Use it in the gap periods, or any time the cycle itself is the thing that's draining.",
